cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use claude-warden in your research or tooling, please cite it as below."
title: claude-warden
abstract: >
  Security hooks and token-saving middleware for Claude Code. Enforces
  network security boundaries, prevents data exfiltration, applies quiet
  command overrides, compresses large MCP outputs, and ships an OpenTelemetry
  observability stack with Grafana dashboards.
version: "0.4.0"
date-released: "2026-03-08"
